thread.title: EastEnders

author: Fiona Flynn
title: EastEnders
text: Hope you've all recovered from the high drama that was Tuesday night's episode. We left things on the cliffhanger of Ian seeing his mum for the first time and while the pair rejoice in seeing each other tonight, the reunion takes a sudden turn. How will a fragile Ian cope with the news that his mother has actually been alive all these years? Meanwhile, the truth about Jason sinks in for Elaine and she's furious with Babe, naturally enough. Although in fairness, she had a lucky escape really thanks to Babe's meddling... we doubt she will see it like that though
